WEBVTT

00:00:28.458 --> 00:00:32.656
I intuitively felt
that I had to find out who they were.

00:00:33.379 --> 00:00:37.196
Questioning a nurse
a day later, she said to me,

00:00:37.220 --> 00:00:40.173
"Oh, you're talking about the threesome."

00:00:40.197 --> 00:00:41.378
(Laughter)

00:00:41.402 --> 00:00:42.934
I was intrigued.

00:00:42.958 --> 00:00:45.703
(Laughter)

00:00:45.727 --> 00:00:49.823
The trio set out on a daily adventure
to coffee and doughnut shops,

00:00:49.847 --> 00:00:51.780
bus stops and street corners.

00:00:52.188 --> 00:00:56.133
I soon learned that the purpose
of these outings was solace

00:00:56.157 --> 00:00:58.014
and a search for meaning.

00:00:58.038 --> 00:01:01.268
The trio sought to combat their alienation